{"tid":1019482,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家信唔信有\"瞳術\"(日本) 或者降頭眼 (南洋)?","createTime":"2019-02-13T03:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T09:26:25.000Z","uid":65346,"like":5,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"37f2fe085013528a2f4243823ea89f8626e4818e","tid":1019482,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:36:18.000Z","msg":"以下內容大家平常心,或當神怪小說角度去睇算了 (估到一定有人大叫~青山走犯 !)<br />\n<br />\n我利申自己嘅睇法先..<br />\n我某程度係信有詛咒同降頭<br />\n回想我自己經歷,自身個人同埋以外嘅人<br />\n最近有一個例子<br />\n公司有個狗公,生得一對降頭眼,一把降頭聲<br />\n見習入職已經用鍚安教個牌頭叫女同事飲雙氧水(降頭水)<br />\n結果又有人(女上司)飲左就信哂佢...<br />\n廿年後,條降頭佬就升左職...<br />\n<br />\n而我自己應該係日式&quot;瞳術&quot;果派<br />\n我感覺自己可以用視力去改變別人命運<br />\n搬運自身衰運去身邊人,寄存再飛向指定 Target (似飛頭降)<br />\n2047 大限,大下跌,樓市全滅都係我成名作 (淡市降)<br />\n<br />\n估唔到~ 香港降頭大戰已經開始了 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f96eb586353c21ffa919104ce6751457aa7b339","tid":1019482,"uid":48631,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"佢落乜撚野降頭咁撚廢要廿年後先升職"},{"pid":"0a696b7263524f6b58005251b5c456e928e40793","tid":1019482,"uid":65346,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"2f96eb586353c21ffa919104ce6751457aa7b339","tid":1019482,"uid":48631,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"佢落乜撚野降頭咁撚廢要廿年後先升職"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"因為有我抗衡...."},{"pid":"e9d663c278d964a8815be973cdf60663f617e207","tid":1019482,"uid":161990,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:42:03.000Z","msg":"青山走犯"},{"pid":"0f8b63e09beeabf9bbac4e6c9f67dd15f126d0bb","tid":1019482,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"一個正常人有能力<br />\n應該去改變社會被扭曲嘅野 (香港樓價)<br />\n唔應該只係用作呃蝦條..<br />\n我呢度講,不出 5 年...<br />\n條死南洋第一邪降 (淫降)佬<br />\n一定又盲又啞 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d46b1cd5508649a6926fcc6cb303f3ac564c0bb","tid":1019482,"uid":114271,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:45:02.000Z","msg":"我覺 成日望住d女仔佢地都急急腳走<br />\n應該feel到我d瞳術有料"},{"pid":"dcc9c7a409c5058bbc6639ade63831b2279c21c0","tid":1019482,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"3d46b1cd5508649a6926fcc6cb303f3ac564c0bb","tid":1019482,"uid":114271,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:45:02.000Z","msg":"我覺 成日望住d女仔佢地都急急腳走<br />\n應該feel到我d瞳術有料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:47:37.000Z","msg":"倒轉吓話...<br />\n好似係上門送生日蛋糕<br />\n再吹個降<br />\n利申:無睇過邪術電視 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ccdf21b443ea24df223160628c8390d74c6866","tid":1019482,"uid":76674,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:48:50.000Z","msg":"你對眼幾多勾玉？"},{"pid":"dd1ab609833edc59f18638a00bcefcc5200ff2ed","tid":1019482,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:53:08.000Z","msg":"連登仔有<del>毒</del>氣功，方圓1米冇異性可以破開個<del>毒</del>氣埸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448f7c0a18cb5ad9e1ae95a964a1da52a7af57d7","tid":1019482,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"32ccdf21b443ea24df223160628c8390d74c6866","tid":1019482,"uid":76674,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:48:50.000Z","msg":"你對眼幾多勾玉？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:54:04.000Z","msg":"我老花就有...<br />\n降術<br />\n唔係x men cyclops<br />\n唔係曹宏威去 9 射死人<br />\n<br />\n係心理+ 精神力 (眼神)<br />\n降頭佬就發揮得淋漓盡